data.description: Location, Location! This is an amazing opportunity for a new owners to call this lovely house your new home! Pretty curb appeal greats you as you pull up to this house which is situated at the end of the street affording you an amazing amount of privacy and calming views of nature. This well loved house is beautifully maintained and is filled with color and character.  Step inside and you will appreciate it's clean and inviting interior. The house has a formal dining and living room option off the foyer with the living room offering 2 sets of french doors to allow privacy if required or opening into the family room for gatherings. The rear of the house is open concept kitchen great room along with a powder bath and mud laundry room and access to the garage. This space is light filled thanks to a kitchen garden window and 2 sets patio doors, one opens onto a spacious deck or the second into a huge enclosed porch with ceiling fan and skylights and framing a view of the privacy to be enjoyed throughout the year.  The kitchen finishes are stunning-with no expense spared to offer the "cook" a space to create...gorgeous cabinetry, stone counters with a carved farm style sink, breakfast bar, stainless appliances including a pot filler, wall ovens with warming drawer and wine fridge, glass front fridge and pantry. There is also space for a table for casual dining. The feature wall fireplace creates a inviting vibe to sit back and relax. Upstairs are four bedrooms  with one being a comfortable owners suite designed with a luxury hotel in mind with dramatic lighting, built-in furniture and a jetted tub. The additional bedrooms are spacious and all offer beautiful hardwoods, one room is currently outfitted as a walk in closet. The main bath offers a double vanity and tub shower combo. If you are looking for a one of a kind home with exceptional details and nature as your neighbor this property delivers.  A quiet setting with an ideal location-mins to major roads, shopping, and more!
